name: 주인공
dialog: Hey guys, hi!

name: 주인공
dialog: Let's have fun today instead of exercising.

name: Himchan
dialog: I agree! What should we do then?

name: Nari
dialog: How about trying traditional games? Like Jegichagi, Yutnori, and Yeon-naligi.

name: Nari
dialog: Oh, I just remembered! Let's play Four Square.

name: 주인공
dialog: Four Square? What kind of game is that?

name: Himchan
dialog: Four Square is a game played by drawing a play board on the floor.

name: Himchan
dialog: First, draw a square play board on the ground and write numbers from 1 to 8 inside it.

name: Himchan
dialog: Prepare a small stone each and start the game.

name: Himchan
dialog: The winner of the rock-paper-scissors puts the stone in the number 1 square.

name: Himchan
dialog: And then, starting from number 2 square, each P_name jumps to the next square in one step.

name: Himchan
dialog: If you step on the line or fall, you're out!

name: Himchan
dialog: Then, the chance goes to the next person.

name: Himchan
dialog: If you succeed, throw the stone to the number 2 square and jump to the last square again.
비고: Q. 컷툰 이미지가 사방치기이미지랑 힘찬이랑 나리가 시범?을 보이는 이미지 2개만 있는데 이대로 연출하면 되나요?

name: Himchan
dialog: Repeat this eight times to succeed!

name: Himchan
dialog: The successful person turns around and throws the stone, taking the square where the stone landed.

name: Himchan
dialog: At the end of the game, the person who occupies the most squares wins. Hahaha.

name: Himchan
dialog: Since Four Square is played by jumping on one foot, you can improve your sense of balance.

name: Himchan
dialog: Who do you think will win among us? Let's try it out now!

name: end
